Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:36.94,0:06:37.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)}嗯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:39.47,0:06:40.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)}總覺得
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:41.08,0:06:43.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)}感覺擰抹布時的動作很像我媽媽
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:44.52,0:06:47.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)}說不定綾波你很適合當家庭主婦呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:51.70,0:06:52.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)}你在胡說什麼啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:54.81,0:06:58.95,TV,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)}[TV]你說什麼！那時候不就是你提出要分手的嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:00.22,0:07:03.20,TV,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)}[TV]那時是我一時糊塗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:03.62,0:07:04.93,TV,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)}[TV]你現在怎麼這麼說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:05.80,0:07:09.28,TV,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)}[TV]我不知道你怎麼樣，但我比以前改變了很多啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:09.76,0:07:12.02,TV,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)}[TV]只是我對你的感覺一直沒變
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:12.03,0:07:15.16,TV,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)}[TV]時針和人一樣，都是不能回到起點重來的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:15.74,0:07:17.80,TV,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)}[TV]我也一樣已經不可能回到那個時候了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:18.05,0:07:19.80,TV,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)}[TV]但是我還是喜歡你——
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:19.90,0:07:21.90,TV,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)}[TV]我都說了我們是不可能的了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:22.28,0:07:25.28,TV,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)}[TV]我為了忘記你足足用了3年的時間
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:25.29,0:07:27.50,TV,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)}[TV]現在什麼都不要說了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:57.62,0:06:58.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)}我回來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:59.04,0:07:00.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)}歡迎回來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:00.56,0:07:03.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)}還不去睡覺嗎？明天你不是有約會嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:03.88,0:07:05.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)}是啊，跟一個大帥哥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:06.23,0:07:07.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)}啊，對了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:07.98,0:07:09.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)}那個借我，熏衣草香水
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:10.34,0:07:10.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)}不行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:11.33,0:07:12.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)}哼！小氣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:13.28,0:07:14.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)}那不是小孩子擦的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:15.50,0:07:16.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)}真嗣在房間裡嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:16.65,0:07:17.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)}一直關在裡面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:18.32,0:07:19.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)}看來他是不願意去見他爸爸嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:20.35,0:07:22.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)}不想見面的話，直說好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:22.14,0:07:23.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)}日本人真是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:24.34,0:07:26.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)}他也不是真的不願意
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:27.08,0:07:28.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)}這才是問題所在
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:34.43,0:07:34.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)}滾回去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:39.76,0:07:41.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)}你做得很好，真嗣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:45.29,0:07:47.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)}真嗣君，我要開門羅
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:52.58,0:07:55.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)}害怕嗎？怕跟你父親單獨見面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:57.41,0:07:58.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)}不可以老是逃避
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:59.31,0:08:00.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)}自己不主動跨出第一步的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:01.15,0:08:02.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)}什麼也不會改變的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:02.96,0:08:04.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)}我知道了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:05.38,0:08:06.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)}從現在起就該好好想想
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:07.08,0:08:08.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)}不只是最初的開始
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:09.04,0:08:11.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)}之後的事情也很重要
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:12.36,0:08:15.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)}總之，你明天去時要挺起胸膛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:15.60,0:08:16.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)}因為你也要見你媽媽啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:17.85,0:08:18.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)}那麼，晚安了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:25.26,0:08:27.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)}你買了明天穿的衣服對吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:27.60,0:08:28.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)}讓我看看嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:28.30,0:08:30.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)}你想看？很貴的喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:30.54,0:08:32.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)}品味比價格更重要
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:32.20,0:08:33.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)}這你就不用擔心了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:34.34,0:08:37.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)}果然…是為了迎合加持先生的喜好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:37.77,0:08:38.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)}哪有可能
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:38.84,0:08:39.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)}早就沒那事兒了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:41.51,0:08:41.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:42.02,0:08:42.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出發吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:42.57,0:08:43.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:49.82,0:08:51.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)}將三個袋子置於內心…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:49.82,0:08:54.60,BGS,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)}*人生中有三個重要的袋：胃(胃袋)、容忍(堪忍袋)、媽媽(袋)
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:52.08,0:08:54.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)}紅色、藍色、黃色的…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:55.28,0:08:57.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)}啊，各位請自便
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:57.40,0:08:58.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,【加持良治先生】
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:00.08,0:09:01.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)}小良沒有來呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:01.63,0:09:05.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)}那個笨蛋從來沒有一次準時過的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:05.52,0:09:06.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)}那是約會的時候吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:06.96,0:09:08.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)}工作時可就不一樣了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:08.74,0:09:09.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)}哎呀，兩位小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:10.20,0:09:11.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)}今天比平常更加美麗耶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:12.62,0:09:14.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)}工作很忙，現在都還是分不開身啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:14.83,0:09:17.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)}明明平常四處閒逛總是很閒的樣子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:18.12,0:09:19.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)}其它就算了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:19.09,0:09:20.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)}但你那那臉鬍渣不能想辦法處理一下嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:21.32,0:09:22.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)}{\a1}你看，領帶都歪了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:22.13,0:09:23.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)}{\a3}哦，果然
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:23.76,0:09:25.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)}真是謝謝你了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:25.57,0:09:26.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)}看起來很像夫妻哦，你們兩個
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:27.86,0:09:29.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)}你說得太對了，小律
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:29.63,0:09:30.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)}誰會跟這種傢伙像夫婦啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:45.92,0:09:47.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)}相隔{\rED} 3 {\r}年了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:47.06,0:09:48.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)}離我們上次一起到這裡來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:49.60,0:09:51.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)}我那時候逃了出去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:52.95,0:09:54.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)}之後就再沒來過
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:54.98,0:09:56.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)}當時我不能明白為何媽媽長眠於此
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:57.59,0:10:00.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)}…現在卻連面容也記不清了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:01.06,0:10:03.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)}人類必須忘記回憶才能活下去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:04.15,0:10:06.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)}但是有些事則是絕對不能忘的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:07.27,0:10:09.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)}唯讓我知道了那個無可取代的事物
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:10.67,0:10:13.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)}我就是為了確認這件事而來到這裡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:15.85,0:10:17.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)}沒有照片之類的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:17.41,0:10:18.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)}我沒有留
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:18.86,0:10:20.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)}這個墓地也只是裝飾品而已
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:20.97,0:10:21.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)}裡面沒有遺體
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:21.90,0:10:23.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)}跟老師說的一樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:23.75,0:10:25.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)}你把一切都捨棄了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:25.98,0:10:27.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)}一切都存在於內心中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:28.03,0:10:28.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)}現在只要這樣就夠了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:32.47,0:10:34.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)}時間到了，我先回去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:42.17,0:10:42.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)}爸爸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:44.96,0:10:45.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)}那個…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:46.21,0:10:47.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)}我今天很高興
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:48.38,0:10:49.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)}可以跟爸爸說話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:50.32,0:10:50.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)}是嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:36.21,0:11:39.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)}拉得不錯嘛，你還有這手啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:40.02,0:11:42.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)}從{\rED} 5 {\r}歲開始拉，到現在才有這種程度
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:43.46,0:11:44.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)}也算不上有什麼天賦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:45.11,0:11:47.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)}貴在堅持啊，我對你有點刮目相看了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:48.31,0:11:51.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)}是老師叫我學的，其實放棄也無所謂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:52.17,0:11:53.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)}那你幹嗎還一直練到現在啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:54.76,0:11:56.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)}又沒人叫我停呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:56.85,0:11:58.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)}果然哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:59.01,0:11:59.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)}這麼早就回來了啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:00.75,0:12:02.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)}還以為你要吃了晚飯再回來呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:02.71,0:12:04.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)}是那男生太無聊了嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:04.81,0:12:08.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)}所以就趁等雲霄飛車的時候溜回來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:04.81,0:12:08.41,BGS,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)}*雲霄飛車（jet coaster）：一種飛行遊戲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:09.37,0:12:10.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)}也不用這麼絕吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:11.23,0:12:14.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)}啊～　理想的男人只有加持一個呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:16.47,0:12:18.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)}你這是說的什麼話呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:18.95,0:12:20.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)}我去一下洗手間
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:21.11,0:12:22.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)}別找借口溜走哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:27.88,0:12:28.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)}高跟鞋…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:29.89,0:12:32.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)}好多年沒有{\rED} 3 {\r}個人在一起喝酒了呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:33.07,0:12:35.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)}美里會不會喝太多了？總覺得她今天話特別多
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:36.91,0:12:39.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)}平時她會為了壓抑自己浮動的心情而喝
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:40.87,0:12:41.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)}而今天正好相反啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:42.75,0:12:46.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)}不愧是曾經一起住過，說出來的話感受就是不同
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:46.85,0:12:51.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)}雖說曾經一起住過，但那時葛城可不穿高跟鞋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:51.57,0:12:54.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)}在學生時代那可是不敢想像的東西啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:54.61,0:12:55.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)}我也是個小鬼…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:56.50,0:12:59.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)}與其說是同居，不如說只是單純的住在一起吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:59.92,0:13:00.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)}僅此而已
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:01.35,0:13:02.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)}現實生活並沒有那麼單純
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:03.37,0:13:04.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)}對了，這個給你，一點小意思
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:05.87,0:13:06.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)}啊，謝謝你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:07.12,0:13:07.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)}真有心啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:08.20,0:13:10.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)}只有對女性，工作就馬馬虎虎了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:10.80,0:13:13.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)}真的嗎？那對美里呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:13.95,0:13:17.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)}已經敗過一次了，我的原則是不打沒勝算的仗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:17.76,0:13:19.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)}我倒覺得你有勝算
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:19.57,0:13:20.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)}那小律你呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:20.82,0:13:22.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)}我的原則是不談自己的事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:23.22,0:13:24.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)}因為無趣嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:25.50,0:13:26.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)}葛城真慢啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:27.15,0:13:28.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)}該不會是去重新化妝了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:29.81,0:13:31.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)}到京都幹什麼去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:32.32,0:13:34.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)}啊？這個土產是松代的啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:34.73,0:13:35.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)}少跟我裝糊塗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:36.11,0:13:37.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)}好奇心太重當心引火燒身哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:38.90,0:13:40.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)}這是作為朋友的忠告
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:41.47,0:13:42.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)}我洗耳恭聽
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:43.20,0:13:44.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)}如果一定要燒身的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:44.56,0:13:45.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)}{\pos(460,446)}我倒是想和你一起玩火
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:45.42,0:13:47.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)}{\a1}那就去買好焰火再說吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:47.78,0:13:48.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)}你回來啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:48.66,0:13:50.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)}你這種輕浮真是一點都沒變啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:51.14,0:13:52.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)}不，我變了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:52.72,0:13:54.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)}活著就表示在變化呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:55.26,0:13:57.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)}正如自我平衡與瞬態平衡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:55.26,0:13:57.27,BGS,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)}*homeostasis(自我平衡)和transisstasis(瞬態平衡)
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:57.92,0:13:58.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)}什麼意思
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:58.95,0:14:01.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)}維持現狀之力與改變現狀之力
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:02.05,0:14:05.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)}同時擁有這兩種矛盾性質的東西才稱為生物
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:06.33,0:14:07.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)}是指男人和女人啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:08.63,0:14:11.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)}閒聊到此結束，我還有工作要做
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:11.61,0:14:12.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)}是嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:12.43,0:14:12.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)}嗯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:12.87,0:14:13.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)}真可惜啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:14.10,0:14:14.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)}再見
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:15.43,0:14:15.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)}嗯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:23.05,0:14:24.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)}嗨，是小真嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:24.47,0:14:27.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)}是我啦，現在在和加持君喝酒呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:28.35,0:14:29.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)}對，今晚第{\rED} 3 {\r}回了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:30.19,0:14:32.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)}好的——好的，再見
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:33.32,0:14:33.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)}是美里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:34.33,0:14:36.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)}嗯，她要晚點回來，叫我們先睡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:37.14,0:14:40.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)}哎？這豈不是要到明天早上才回來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:40.40,0:14:42.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)}怎麼可能？加持先生跟她在一起啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:42.95,0:14:45.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)}你是白癡嗎？所以才會啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:51.28,0:14:53.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)}年紀都不小了別像個小孩一樣嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:53.50,0:14:56.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)}真不好意思啊，都這個歲數了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:56.36,0:14:57.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)}彼此彼此我也差不多
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:57.99,0:14:58.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)}是啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:59.49,0:15:01.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)}葛城你都穿上高跟鞋了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:02.41,0:15:03.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)}時光的流逝真是好快啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:04.79,0:15:07.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)}鬍渣去刮掉嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:07.79,0:15:08.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)}是、是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:09.75,0:15:11.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)}讓我下來走，謝謝
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:11.79,0:15:12.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)}嗯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:16.73,0:15:19.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)}加持君，我變了嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:20.81,0:15:21.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)}…變漂亮了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:24.06,0:15:27.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)}對不起，那時我單方面的要求分手
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:28.00,0:15:30.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)}我還說喜歡上了別人…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:31.03,0:15:31.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)}那是——騙你的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:32.44,0:15:32.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)}你看穿了嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:33.46,0:15:33.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)}沒有
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:37.11,0:15:38.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)}我發覺了…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:39.33,0:15:41.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)}加持君你很像我的父親…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:45.09,0:15:49.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)}我…想在其他男人的身上尋找父親的影子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:50.31,0:15:53.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)}當我發覺這點時…我好怕
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:53.87,0:15:55.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)}害怕得不得了…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:56.57,0:15:58.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)}和加持君在一起的事也是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:59.07,0:16:03.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)}連我自己是個女人這點…都令我害怕
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:05.32,0:16:09.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)}憎恨父親的我卻喜歡上像父親的男人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:10.42,0:16:12.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)}後來想要斬斷一切而選擇了{\rED} NERV{\r}…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:13.96,0:16:16.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)}但是，這也是父親所參與過的組織
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:16.91,0:16:21.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)}最後只能用向使徒復仇這樣的借口來搪塞人們
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:26.87,0:16:30.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)}這是葛城你自己的選擇，不用向我道歉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:31.53,0:16:34.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)}不是的！這不是我選擇的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:34.30,0:16:36.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)}這只是為了逃避
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:36.65,0:16:39.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)}我只是想從「父親」這個咒縛下逃避而已…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:39.44,0:16:41.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)}和真嗣一樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:41.97,0:16:43.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)}都是膽小鬼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:44.61,0:16:45.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)}真的很抱歉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:46.00,0:16:48.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)}現在才趁著酒勢講這些話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:48.70,0:16:49.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)}夠了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:49.52,0:16:51.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)}我真是個小孩子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:51.02,0:16:53.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)}根本沒資格說真嗣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:53.74,0:16:54.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)}夠了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:54.29,0:16:59.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)}而且我還是個只會在需要時才想依靠男人的狡滑女人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:59.68,0:17:02.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)}或許我那時候就是單純地在利用加持君罷了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:03.01,0:17:03.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)}真令人作嘔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:03.67,0:17:04.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)}夠了！不要再說了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:05.11,0:17:06.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)}真是對自己感到絕望啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:30.45,0:17:31.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)}…喂，真嗣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:31.66,0:17:32.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)}來接吻吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:32.74,0:17:34.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)}嗯，什麼事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:34.60,0:17:35.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)}接吻啦，接吻
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:36.15,0:17:37.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)}你還沒接過吻吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:38.08,0:17:38.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)}嗯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:39.23,0:17:39.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)}那就來啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:40.93,0:17:41.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)}為什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:41.77,0:17:42.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)}無聊嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:43.16,0:17:45.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)}就因為無聊…哪有這樣的…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:46.08,0:17:48.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)}因為是母親的忌日所以不想和女生接吻
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:49.49,0:17:51.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)}擔心她可能會在天上看到嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:52.20,0:17:52.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)}不是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:52.74,0:17:53.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)}還是因為你害怕
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:54.10,0:17:56.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)}我才不怕呢！不過是接個吻而已
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:56.46,0:17:58.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)}牙齒刷過了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:58.95,0:17:59.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)}嗯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:59.58,0:18:00.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)}那…開始嘍
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:10.74,0:18:12.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)}你鼻子呼氣弄得我好癢，摒住
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:57.75,0:19:01.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)}果然不該用這辦法來打發時間
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:05.82,0:19:07.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)}好了到了，堅持住
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:10.53,0:19:11.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)}加持先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:11.47,0:19:14.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)}哎——　！加持先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:11.47,0:19:14.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)}{\pos(296,452)\fs40\b1\fnMS Mincho}♡{\r}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:18.19,0:19:20.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)}那麼，我要回去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:20.75,0:19:22.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)}加持先生也在這裡住一晚吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:22.68,0:19:24.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)}這副樣子我明天出去要被人笑死的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:25.15,0:19:27.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)}哎——沒關係嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:28.20,0:19:31.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)}哎呀，加持先生你真是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:31.21,0:19:31.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)}…再見嘍
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:36.49,0:19:38.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)}薰衣草的香味…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:39.56,0:19:41.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)}不好意思，葛城就拜託你們倆照顧了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:42.40,0:19:42.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)}好的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:43.39,0:19:44.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)}那麼，晚安
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:44.41,0:19:45.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)}晚安
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:48.30,0:19:50.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)}怎麼了？垂頭喪氣的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:50.70,0:19:52.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)}就因為跟你這種人接吻了啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:54.10,0:19:57.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)}那麼接下來由女生回答
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:57.44,0:19:58.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)}綾波
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:59.77,0:20:01.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)}綾波今天又請假了啊
