Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:45.56,0:20:46.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)}托你的福總算醒過來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:47.04,0:20:47.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)}那真是太好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:48.28,0:20:49.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)}這就是你真正的工作
